      propertyPath: 'dialogueLines.Array.data[0]'
      value: (I looked at the gravestone. It looked peaceful in the sunlight)
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4654630718448193217, guid: f7232d8a3299b4b539ed091b8ce5451a, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueLines.Array.data[1]'
      value: (I took the old flowers and replaced them with the new bouquet)
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4654630718448193217, guid: f7232d8a3299b4b539ed091b8ce5451a, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueLines.Array.data[2]'
      value: (I had never been fond of graveyards, but it felt calming in a way)
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4654630718448193217, guid: f7232d8a3299b4b539ed091b8ce5451a, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueLines.Array.data[3]'
      value: (I put my paw on the gravestone and smiled)
